name: Field_Dylan
description:
One of the many things I'm thankful for is how global Figma's community is, and I wanted my quilt to represent this!

This was a stretch challenge for me (and I was in a rush at the end) so apologies if I messed any countries up really bad!!

Also, shout out to https://www.figma.com/user/804170841566687549/Diego for making a variant of this concept for their quilt! I saw Diego's submission as I was making mine and it was comforting to know we were both in this one together ;) Diego, hope to meet you at Config and find out what else we share in common!
